\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\lang english
6.1 Knowledge Base as System of Record
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
Redmine is the authoritative System of Record for all KB content.
 All KB articles shall be stored in Redmine as the primary repository.
 The Assistant IT Director shall maintain at least one secondary accessible medium synchronized no less than monthly.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\lang english
6.2 KB Content Categories
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
All knowledge artifacts shall be classified under the following categories:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
